HEADWORD: Rheum
<hw>Rhe"um</hw> <pr>(r⟦emac⟧"⟦ucr⟧m)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
from L. <ets>Rha</ets> the river Volga, on the banks of which it grows.
